		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well I'm no pro in 6502, but I managed to crack one out for it. This worked for me on both variations of Punch-Out! So it ought to work for others too.
<br />
<br />Download <a href="http://webpages.charter.net/bootgod/PXROM.zip" class="postlink">PXROM.ZIP</a>
<br />EDIT: Includes source now

		

		</td>
