	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Quietust wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">No source included?</div>
<br />
<br />I originally based this off of a few other of kevtris's plugins, but I decided to rewrite it to make it easier to understand. The above zip includes source now.
<br />
<br />One thing to note is there is no ROM size detection, I figured it was unneccessary considering only Punch-Out! uses it, so it assumes 128K PRG and 128K CHR.
<br />
<br />I think the source could very easily be changed for MMC4, but I have no MMC4 carts to test it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
